---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>🌱 Welcome to Pixel Valley Devlog</h1>
			<div class="game-intro">
				<p>Hello there! I'm on an exciting journey to create a Stardew Valley-inspired farming simulation game. This devlog will document my progress, challenges, and discoveries as I build this game from the ground up.</p>
				
				<h2>📜 Latest Updates</h2>
				<ul class="update-list">
					<li><a href="/devlog/first-steps">Getting Started: Laying the Foundation</a></li>
					<li><a href="/devlog/character-design">Character Design & Animation</a></li>
					<li><a href="/devlog/farming-mechanics">Implementing Farming Mechanics</a></li>
				</ul>

				<h2>🎮 About the Game</h2>
				<p>Inspired by the charm of Stardew Valley, my game will feature:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>🌾 Farming and crop cultivation</li>
					<li>🏡 Farm customization and expansion</li>
					<li>👥 Villager relationships and events</li>
					<li>⛏️ Mining and exploration</li>
					<li>📜 Engaging storyline and quests</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>🔧 Development Stack</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Game Engine: Godot</li>
					<li>Art: Aseprite for pixel art</li>
					<li>Music & SFX: BFXR, LMMS</li>
					<li>Devlog: Astro</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>📅 Development Roadmap</h2>
				<ol>
					<li>Core farming mechanics</li>
					<li>Character movement and interactions</li>
					<li>Day/Night cycle and seasons</li>
					<li>Villager AI and relationships</li>
					<li>Mining and combat systems</li>
				</ol>

				<p>Follow along as I turn this dream into reality, one pixel at a time!</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
